ZH: 不经常锻炼身体会导致健康问题。
EN: Not exercising regularly can lead to health issues.

ZH: 不经过考虑就做决定通常是不明智的。
EN: Making decisions without careful consideration is usually unwise.

ZH: 她不经过任何人帮助就成功了。
EN: She succeeded without anyone's help.

ZH: 他总是不经思考就说出自己的想法。
EN: He always voices his thoughts without thinking.

ZH: 不经世事的人很难理解人生的复杂性。
EN: People who lack life experience find it difficult to understand the complexity of life.

ZH: 这是一个不经过修改的初稿。
EN: This is a first draft without any revisions.

ZH: 孩子不经父母指导容易走上错误的道路。
EN: Children can easily go astray without parental guidance.

ZH: 这个故事是根据真实事件改编的，但并不经过写实。
EN: This story is adapted from true events, but it is not realistic.

ZH: 别看他平常不经心，他对工作可是认真的。
EN: Despite appearing careless at times, he is serious about his work.

ZH: 我们不经国境线就可以通过电话和视频联系。
EN: We can stay in touch through phone calls and video chats without crossing borders.

ZH: 张主任批准了你的休假请求，不经审核。
EN: Director Zhang approved your leave request without going through the review process.

ZH: 请不要随意修改文档，不经过授权就不可以更改内容。
EN: Please do not modify the document at will. The content cannot be changed without authorization.

ZH: 他不经解释就退出了工作岗位。
EN: He resigned from his job without explaining.

ZH: 这个项目不经投资者同意就无法进行。
EN: The project cannot proceed without the consent of the investors.

ZH: 学生必须不经过外教许可，不得随意离开教室。
EN: Students must not leave the classroom without the permission of the foreign teacher.

ZH: 世界上没有不经过努力就能够成功的人。
EN: There is no one in the world who can succeed without effort.

ZH: 他不经过检查就买了这辆二手车。
EN: He bought this used car without getting it inspected.

ZH: 她总是不经思考就发脾气。
EN: She always loses her temper without thinking.

ZH: 不经过实践，知识就是空谈。
EN: Without practice, knowledge is just idle talk.

ZH: 如果不经用户允许，我们不能擅自使用他们的个人信息。
EN: We cannot use users' personal information without their permission.

ZH: 不经过父母同意，他们不能出远门。
EN: They cannot go far without their parents' permission.
